                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="page-content">
        <div class="container">
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="page-header">
                <h1 class="page-title">Community Updates</h1>
                <p class="page-description">
                    Stay informed with the latest news and developments regarding the truck stop proposal and our community action efforts.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Alert Section for Latest Update -->
            <section class="alert-section">
                <div class="alert-card">
                    <div class="alert-content">
                        <i data-lucide="alert-triangle" class="alert-icon"></i>
                        <div class="alert-text">
                            <h3 class="alert-title">URGENT: Village Ordinance Passed - Action Needed</h3>
                            <p class="alert-description">
                                The <strong>Village of Lemont</strong> has officially passed an ordinance on <strong>August 11, 2025</strong> 
                                to annex four unincorporated properties on Lemont Road. These properties are now under Lemont's jurisdiction 
                                and the next step could be a rezoning request from residential to commercial.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Updates List -->
            <div class="meetings-list">
                <div class="meeting-card urgent">
                    <div class="meeting-header">
                        <div class="meeting-icon-wrapper">
                            <i data-lucide="alert-triangle" class="meeting-icon"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="meeting-title-section">
                            <div class="meeting-title-row">
                                <h3 class="meeting-title">Village Ordinance Passed</h3>
                                <span class="urgent-badge">URGENT</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="meeting-type">August 11, 2025</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="meeting-description">
                        <p>The Village of Lemont has officially passed an ordinance to annex four unincorporated properties on Lemont Road. These properties are now under Lemont's jurisdiction and the next step could be a rezoning request from residential to commercial.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="meeting-actions">
                        <a href="petitions.html" class="btn btn-primary">
                            <i data-lucide="file-text"></i>
                            Sign Petition
                        </a>
                        <a href="contacts.html" class="btn btn-outline">
                            <i data-lucide="phone"></i>
                            Contact Officials
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="meeting-card">
                    <div class="meeting-header">
                        <div class="meeting-icon-wrapper">
                            <i data-lucide="users" class="meeting-icon"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="meeting-title-section">
                            <h3 class="meeting-title">Community Meeting Scheduled</h3>
                            <p class="meeting-type">Coming Soon</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="meeting-description">
                        <p>We're organizing a community meeting to discuss our opposition strategy and coordinate our efforts. Date and location details will be announced soon.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="meeting-actions">
                        <a href="meetings.html" class="btn btn-primary">
                            <i data-lucide="users"></i>
                            View Meetings
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="meeting-card">
                    <div class="meeting-header">
                        <div class="meeting-icon-wrapper">
                            <i data-lucide="book-open" class="meeting-icon"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="meeting-title-section">
                            <h3 class="meeting-title">New Research Materials Available</h3>
                            <p class="meeting-type">Recently Added</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="meeting-description">
                        <p>We've compiled comprehensive research on health, environmental, and safety concerns related to gas stations and truck stops. Download PDFs with citations and share with neighbors.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="meeting-actions">
                        <a href="information.html" class="btn btn-primary">
                            <i data-lucide="book-open"></i>
                            View Research
                        </a>
                        <a href="flyers.html" class="btn btn-outline">
                            <i data-lucide="download"></i>
                            Download Materials
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Action Cards Section -->
            <div class="main-content">
                <h2 class="section-title">Take Action Now</h2>
                <div class="action-cards">
                    <a href="petitions.html" class="action-card">
                        <div class="action-icon-wrapper">
                            <i data-lucide="file-signature" class="action-icon"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="action-content">
                            <h4 class="action-title">Sign Petitions</h4>
                            <p class="action-description">Add your voice to our community petitions opposing the development.</p>
                        </div>
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="action-arrow"></i>
                    </a>

                    <a href="contacts.html" class="action-card">
                        <div class="action-icon-wrapper action-icon-secondary">
                            <i data-lucide="phone-call" class="action-icon"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="action-content">
                            <h4 class="action-title">Contact Officials</h4>
                            <p class="action-description">Reach out to village board members and express your concerns.</p>
                        </div>
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="action-arrow"></i>
                    </a>

                    <a href="flyers.html" class="action-card">
                        <div class="action-icon-wrapper">
                            <i data-lucide="share-2" class="action-icon"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="action-content">
                            <h4 class="action-title">Spread the Word</h4>
                            <p class="action-description">Download flyers and share information with your neighbors.</p>
                        </div>
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="action-arrow"></i>
                    </a>

                    <a href="meetings.html" class="action-card">
                        <div class="action-icon-wrapper action-icon-secondary">
                            <i data-lucide="calendar-check" class="action-icon"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="action-content">
                            <h4 class="action-title">Attend Meetings</h4>
                            <p class="action-description">Join community meetings and village board sessions.</p>
                        </div>
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="action-arrow"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Call to Action -->
            <section class="cta-section">
                <div class="cta-content">
                    <h3 class="cta-title">Stay Updated</h3>
                    <p class="cta-description">
                        Get the latest updates delivered directly to your inbox. We'll keep you informed about meetings, 
                        developments, and action opportunities.
                    </p>
                    <div class="cta-buttons">
                        <a href="information.html" class="btn btn-hero">Learn More</a>
                        <a href="petitions.html" class="btn btn-outline">Sign Petition</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

